        {
            "title": "銅鑼灣過路婦捱貨Van撞 右腿被輾骨折送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"銅鑼灣過路婦捱貨Van撞 右腿被輾骨折送院\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/8f218ec0cb9793901c00a738594bfe05/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050822581511868.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">銅鑼灣過路婦捱貨Van撞 右腿被輾骨折送院</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>銅鑼灣景隆街，今日（5月8日）晚上9時許，一部輕型貨車轉入謝斐道時，撞倒一名過路老婦，並輾過老婦右腿。救護員接報趕至發現老婦骨折浴血，隨即將其送往瑪麗醫院救治。警方亦到場跟進意外，向輕貨男司機女乘客問話，調查事發原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4238014/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"涉事輕型貨車。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d42b45f5dde7d903a83d90b8c0f38d5/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250508_223630828_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉事輕型貨車。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4238015/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方亦到場跟進意外，向輕貨男司機女乘客問話。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4418bd6e310ca59c38663637ff40d676/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250508_223630828_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方亦到場跟進意外，向輕貨男司機女乘客問話。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2067986/即時-港聞-銅鑼灣過路婦捱貨Van撞-右腿被輾骨折送院",
